 Objective:
Be the first player to reach tile 100 by rolling the dice and moving your token across the board. Avoid the snakes and climb up ladders to get ahead!

Rules:
-Players take turns rolling a six-sided dice (1–6).

-The number you roll is the number of tiles you move forward.

-If you land on the bottom of a ladder, you climb up to the top of it.

-If you land on the head of a snake, you slide down to its tail.

-You must land exactly on tile 100 to win. If your roll goes past it, you stay in the same spot.

-First player to reach tile 100 wins!

Controls:

-Press SPACE to roll the dice on your turn.

-Two players alternate turns.

-You’ll see your name and current tile on the screen.

-After one game, you’ll be asked if you want to play again.

-The program tracks your scores and shows statistics (mean, mode, etc.) if you play multiple rounds!

